title: Mark Minervini - Swing Trading Seminar  (25 March 2015)
description:
Movies : Other : Other quality : English

A recording of the webinar which Mark Minervini and David Ryan gave on 25 March 2015 regarding how to achieve super performance in the stock market.

Both Mark and David are past winners of the US Investing Championship and have both made tens of millions in the stock market over the past several decades.

Enjoy and Seed!!
